SUMMARY:The Great waters Fly Fishing Expo 2026
DESCRIPTION:Our expo is the largest fly fishing event in the region. With vendors from the Midwest and across the country including fly shops\, guides\, top brands\, outfitters and non-profits\, we offer the newest and best in the world of fly fishing. We also place a strong emphasis on fly fishing education and there will be nearly four dozen free programs and seminars\, as well as on-going free casting instruction taking place over the three days of the event. Proceeds benefit the non-profit Minnesota Trout Unlimited.\nExpo Times: \nFriday\, March 13th\, 2026\n1pm-7pm \nSaturday\, March 14th\, 2026\n9am-6pm \nSunday\, March 15th\, 2026\n10am-4pm \nSaturday Social\n6pm – 10pm \nDownload a flyer here:  https://facebook.us12.list-manage.com/track/click?u=c7ff733ff7c90818f17788589&id=a066b1d49f&e=a9047d83aa
URL:https://www.hoosierflyfishers.com/event/the-great-waters-fly-fishing-expo-2026/
LOCATION:Hamline University Walker Fieldhouse\, 1550 Hewitt Ave\, St Paul\, Mn\, 55104
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260914
